profile_summary: Dedicated and detail-oriented Warehouse Assistant with a strong background in warehouse operations and logistics. Proven ability to manage inventory, maintain equipment, and ensure the efficient and timely completion of all warehouse tasks. Committed to maintaining a safe and productive work environment.

Coordinated with logistics team to ensure timely delivery of goods
Ensured adherence to safety protocols to maintain a safe work environment
Worked efficiently to complete all assigned tasks in a timely manner
Collaborated with team members to ensure smooth warehouse operations
achievements: Implemented a new inventory management system that increased efficiency by 20%
